title: Sweden 2 Year Note Yield
description: Sweden 2Y Bond Yield was 2.38 percent on Friday November 11, according to over-the-counter interbank yield quotes for this government bond maturity. Historically, the Sweden 2 Year Note Yield reached an all time high of 4.93 in July of 2008. This page includes a chart with historical data for Sweden 2Y Bond Yield.
